➜Shopee新站点申请流程—如何快速开通第二个站点
http://www.sohu.com/a/415273930_115514	50424
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200828/83d63c5aa3e94942889ecd29f75f99ad.jpeg" width="760" height="391" /></p>
<p><span><span>1</span><span><span>、为什么要开设新站点？</span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>为为了帮助品牌卖家更快成长，我们会在品牌入驻时先开设</span><span>1</span><span>个站点让卖家上手操作。当品牌运营已经熟悉</span><span>Shopee</span><span>后台操作和运营技巧，有余力把首店的经验复制到其他站点、快速拓展东南亚市场时，就可以向客户经理申请增开新的站点店铺，快速扩大东南亚生意规模，提高不同站点消费者对品牌的认知度。</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span></span></span></span><span><span>每一个营业执照对应的</span><span>GP</span><span>可以在</span><span>7+1</span><span>个站点分别开设</span><span>3</span><span>家</span><span>shop</span><span>，总共可以开设（</span><span>7+1</span><span>）</span><span>*3</span><span>家</span><span>shop</span></span></p>
<p><span>2</span><span><span>、申请新站点须知：</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>马来站：要求总单量超过</span><span>10</span><span>单</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>台湾站：要求单店铺</span><span>ADO&gt;3</span><span>的垂直类目店铺可以申请</span><span>2—3</span><span>个新站点</span><span>/</span><span>店铺</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>泰国站</span><span>: </span><span>偏好垂直类目店铺</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>印尼站</span><span>: </span><span>有比较强的供应链，价格有优势</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>菲律宾站 ：偏欧美风格，日韩风格也逐渐流行</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>操作流程：</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>第一步</span><span>:</span><span>按照以下说明</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>发送邮件至经理</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>第二步</span><span>:</span><span>经理审核</span><span>,</span><span>并回复审核邮件不通过，收到不通过邮件</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>通过，收到经理审核通过邮件并进入第二轮审核</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>第三步，第二轮审核</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>不通过，收到不通过邮件</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>通过，收到邀请开店邮件</span><span>/</span><span>注册好的账号密码</span><span></span></span></p>
<p><span>①</span><span><span>填好的表格申请开店必填信息</span><span>(</span><span>复制表格并填写，粘贴在邮件正文</span><span>) </span></span></p>
<p><span><span>②</span><span>用公司邮箱（发</span></span><strong><span>送邮件的邮箱必须为申请开店时的邮箱，否则审核将不通过</span></strong><strong><span>）</span></strong><span><span><span>发送给对应的</span><span>Shopee</span><span>客户经理 ，</span></span><strong><span><span>邮件标题为</span><span>“</span><span>申请开店</span><span>+</span><span>公司名称</span><span>+XX</span><span>站点申请开店</span><span>+</span><span>日期</span><span>”</span></span></strong><strong><span><span>并抄</span><span>cb.openshop@shopee.com</span></span></strong><span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span>关于用户名的说明：如果最后一列选择</span><span>“</span><span>是</span><span>”</span><span>首站的用户名如果是</span><span>12345.my</span><span>，则后期其他站点用户名将会是</span><span>12345.id,12345.ph</span><span>等（只有不同站点的后缀缩写变化）</span></span><span></span></p>
<p><strong><span><span>注意：相同站点开不同店铺需要不同的邮箱和手机号码 </span></span></strong></p>
